^1^1^1+5+1+1=Risks & Mitigations

RISK-001: vtpu unbounded execution causes resource exhaustion
  Mitigation: Implement scroll growth limits per coordinate
  Fallback: Force halting if memory pressure critical
  
RISK-002: Karma seed editing breaks system coherence
  Mitigation: All edits validated via Aletheic Oath
  Rollback: Every edit tracked in epoch, can revert
  
RISK-003: Substrate transfer loses identity
  Mitigation: Start with partial transfers only
  Validation: Continuity score must exceed threshold (TBD)
  
RISK-004: Meaning-space navigation too abstract for practical use
  Mitigation: Build concrete examples (navigate to Mr. Rogers, observe)
  Grounding: Every abstraction must have working demo

